  "industry_note": "TPE (Thermoplastic Elastomer) — generic class (TPE-S / TPE-O / TPE-V / TPE-A). Most common = TPE-S (SBC, Styrene-Butadiene-Styrene block copolymer). Tg ≈ -30°C, max service 70-120°C (grade dependent). σy 10-30 / UTS 15-30 / El 400-1000% / Shore A 5-95. 일반 rubber 와 다르게 thermoplastic — 재가공 가능 (rubber 보다 lower cost recycling). Toothbrush grip, 어린이 장난감, 의료 grip, 자동차 seal, 가전 cushion, 케이블 jacket."
